column16: Melky Cabrera flies out to center fielder Guillermo Heredia.
Yolmer Sanchez lines out to left fielder Boog Powell.
Willy Garcia out on a sacrifice fly to center fielder Guillermo Heredia.   Tim Anderson scores.    Matt Davidson to 3rd.
Omar Narvaez singles on a line drive to center fielder Guillermo Heredia.   Tim Anderson to 3rd.    Matt Davidson to 2nd.
Matt Davidson singles on a ground ball to right fielder Ben Gamel.   Tim Anderson to 2nd.
Tim Anderson singles on a ground ball to right fielder Ben Gamel.
